{
  "name": "Precise Strikes",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Hyuga.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Hyūga Clan, Level 8+</p><p>You have learned to use your Gentle fist in conjunction with your Byakugan far more accurately than others of similar level. You gain the following benefits;</p><p>• Increase your Dexterity or Wisdom score by 1, to a maximum of 20</p><p>• Once per casting, when you would deal Chakra damage to a creature as a result of Hyūga Hijutsu, the target must make a Constitution saving throw vs your Taijutsu save DC. On a failed save they lose 1 Tenacity die, if they have any.</p><p>• Once per casting, when you would choose to either Disrupt or Block using a Hyūga clan Hijutsu, if you spend 1 Chakra die, you can use both effects</p><p>• When you would choose to deal damage to a creatures hit points, you increase your [Unarmed Damage] to 2d6. This increases to 3d6 at 11th level</p>",
